WEBVTT

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:35.680
Gang.

00:01:38.759 --> 00:01:39.090
Tomb.

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:05.160
Master.

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:08.240
I haven't visited you in over three years.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:10.500
I've graduated from the police academy.

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:12.720
Winter in Shenyang

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:14.290
is incredibly cold.

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.120
It's bone-chilling.

00:02:16.880 --> 00:02:18.880
The nights are incredibly long too.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:20.840
I once asked my professor

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.820
why the police academy

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:24.800
was built in such a cold place.

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.020
The professor said

00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:29.640
that as criminal police, we have to be like this.

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:30.500
We have to learn

00:02:30.600 --> 00:02:31.800
to walk in the coldest

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.079
and darkest places.

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:35.920
But our hearts cannot grow cold,

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:37.320
our eyes cannot go blind,

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:39.040
and our hands cannot go numb.

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:41.280
We must always firmly believe

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:42.920
that dawn will eventually come.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:43.640
We must even

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:45.360
have the determination

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.360
to bring the dawn out ourselves.

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:49.900
We must never let the darkness

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:50.680
win.

00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:55.440
You think so too, right?

00:02:57.040 --> 00:02:58.120
I believe you do.

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:00.640
You must.

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:05.210
Don't worry.

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:07.440
Me too.

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:33.370
Ma Jinguang.

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:44.680
I didn't do it.

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:45.960
Who is she?

00:06:46.159 --> 00:06:47.040
Why is she here?

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:48.240
Why are you here?

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:49.600
What is going on?

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:51.360
Her name is Wang Hongjia.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:52.680
Zhang Biao's wife.

00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:55.440
I said I didn't do it.

00:06:55.760 --> 00:06:57.960
Why do these things always happen to me?

00:06:58.720 --> 00:06:59.920
What did I do wrong

00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:01.000
for God to treat me like this?

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.480
To make you treat me like this?

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:02.960
Don't come near me.

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:03.560
Stay back.

00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:04.520
Don't come near me.

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:05.680
Stay away from me.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:08.410
If you push me again,

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:09.720
If you push me again,

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:10.440
we will die together.

00:07:10.440 --> 00:07:12.100
I believe you didn't kill her.

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:16.160
I believe you have nothing to do with this.

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.000
But earlier,

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.560
you lied to us.

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.460
You said you went to sell ore that day.

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:22.960
But actually,

00:07:22.960 --> 00:07:24.480
you went to sell explosives.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:26.280
You bought many identical bags.

00:07:26.640 --> 00:07:27.680
The bags you carried that day

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.440
were all used to carry explosives.

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:30.240
So what?

00:07:30.840 --> 00:07:32.320
I didn't blow up Zhang Biao.

00:07:32.320 --> 00:07:33.560
Nor did I kill my wife.

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:36.570
And this woman who suddenly appeared,

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:38.920
I don't even know her.

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.920
The explosive that killed Zhang Biao was made by you.

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:42.720
You knew it when Zhang Biao died.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:43.640
The characteristics were so obvious.

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:44.880
It was all over the street.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:45.960
You kept saying

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:47.080
you wanted to avenge Kong Jiao.

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:48.280
Why didn't you tell us?

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:49.120
Tell you?

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:51.520
Don't you just think I'm a murderer?

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:52.460
That person

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:54.480
said his fruit seedlings were ruined by wild boars.

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:55.960
He bought some explosives from me to deal with the wild boars.

00:07:55.960 --> 00:07:57.400
How could I know he was going to blow someone up?

00:07:57.400 --> 00:07:58.120
What about back then?

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:59.280
Didn't you know back then either?

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:00.340
I just didn't know.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:01.840
I did whatever my dad said.

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:03.770
I had no idea what he was going to do.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.050
You admitted it.

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.250
It really is you.

00:08:16.960 --> 00:08:19.290
The explosives back then were made by you.

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:26.840
I can't clear my name anyway.

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:28.040
You were used.

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:29.920
You were used.

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:32.159
You didn't kill Zhang Biao.

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.159
And you couldn't have killed Kong Jiao either.

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:34.960
As for Wang Hongjia,

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:36.419
you didn't tie her up here.

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:38.480
You were used,

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:40.330
just like back then,

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:42.820
when you were used by your dad.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.960
Who used me?

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:47.880
The person who bought your explosives.

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:49.040
That night,

00:08:49.640 --> 00:08:51.520
he arranged to meet you at the old market for the deal

00:08:51.520 --> 00:08:52.880
just to make you lose

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:54.880
your alibi in the Kong Jiao case.

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:56.770
But he didn't expect

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:57.880
that you happened to go home,

00:08:57.880 --> 00:08:58.920
passed by the surveillance cameras,

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:00.520
and thereby got an alibi.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.520
After kidnapping Wang Hongjia,

00:09:03.520 --> 00:09:05.920
he specially went to the cabin to frame you.

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:06.840
Steel balls,

00:09:06.840 --> 00:09:07.500
a backpack.

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:09.080
He left all the characteristics that could point to you

00:09:09.080 --> 00:09:10.400
there for us to see.

00:09:10.760 --> 00:09:12.920
He knows your habits and whereabouts like the back of his hand.

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:14.360
He knows where you make explosives

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:15.760
and all your secrets.

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:17.640
Why me?

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:19.640
You have a family history of crime.

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:21.720
You know everyone involved in this case.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:23.480
You have a motive to kill Zhang Biao and Kong Jiao.

00:09:23.480 --> 00:09:24.120
What's more,

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:25.680
you also know how to make explosives.

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:27.280
By treating you as a suspect,

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.800
he could get away with it perfectly.

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:29.320
So,

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:30.920
he has been misleading us

00:09:30.920 --> 00:09:32.380
to presume you're guilty.

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:33.960
Can you catch him now

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:35.000
and clear my name?

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.930
Tell me everything that happened,

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:39.100
and I'm confident I can catch him.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:46.560
Do you trust me?

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.730
Why did you come here today?

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:53.440
Did someone tell you to come?

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:05.120
I wanted to get some money to buy Jiaojiao a nice coffin.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:07.380
She suffered too much when she was alive.

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.240
But that thing is too expensive.

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:11.160
It just so happens that someone online said

00:10:11.160 --> 00:10:12.690
they wanted to get some ore.

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.840
I knew this place had been sealed off long ago

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:16.300
and no one was watching it,

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:18.080
so I came.

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:19.890
How did you contact each other?

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:26.000
Yan Mi.

00:11:28.280 --> 00:11:28.800
Yan Mi.

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:33.000
Yan Mi!

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:38.960
Yan!

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:40.240
Yan!

00:11:42.400 --> 00:11:43.400
Save Ma Jinguang.

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:49.290
The case from back then,

00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:50.610
I've figured it out.

00:11:51.520 --> 00:11:52.850
He made the explosives.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:54.840
But he has nothing to do

00:11:55.640 --> 00:11:56.560
with this case.

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:58.080
Yan!

00:11:58.440 --> 00:11:59.640
Yan, you can't sleep!

00:12:01.720 --> 00:12:02.780
Call an ambulance!

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:04.540
Call an ambulance!

00:12:36.680 --> 00:12:38.140
Look at the two of us today.

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:39.280
Whoosh, whoosh, just like that,

00:12:39.280 --> 00:12:41.160
we subdued that knife-wielding thug.

00:12:41.160 --> 00:12:42.220
Aren't we awesome?

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:43.160
The most important thing

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:44.690
is that we cracked the case.

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:47.400
Master.

00:12:47.800 --> 00:12:48.480
Master, today we...

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:50.080
You were too reckless today.

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:54.370
Do you think being a detective is all about hot blood?

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:56.480
Cracking cases is important,

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.880
catching criminals is important,

00:12:57.880 --> 00:13:00.320
but the most important thing is the safety of you and your partner.

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:03.520
The most important thing is that you can come back safely.

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:14.080
I can't.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.450
I can't run anymore.

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:21.810
Three more laps.

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:22.480
Hey.

00:13:24.520 --> 00:13:26.080
Running like you have a death wish.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:27.240
Without excellent stamina,

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:28.500
how can you fight evil?

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:30.040
Keep running.

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:39.560
Master.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.720
How is Brother Yan doing?

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:48.650
They're trying to save him.

00:14:07.320 --> 00:14:08.040
Tell me.

00:14:08.520 --> 00:14:09.450
How is the scene?

00:14:15.560 --> 00:14:16.640
Inside the mine,

00:14:17.080 --> 00:14:19.210
we found Ma Jinguang and Wang Hongjia.

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:22.640
When entering the scene, we smelled

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.080
a sweet burning and sour stench.

00:14:25.680 --> 00:14:28.810
It's the same smell as the scene of Zhang Biao's bombing.

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:29.240
Also,

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:31.200
The motorcycle near the mine,

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:32.330
its tire tracks were

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:33.960
extracted and compared.

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:34.960
They completely match

00:14:34.960 --> 00:14:36.160
the ones we found

00:14:36.160 --> 00:14:37.160
in the cornfield.

00:14:37.240 --> 00:14:38.480
Unfortunately, the license plate is fake.

00:14:38.480 --> 00:14:39.440
We can't trace the owner.

00:14:39.440 --> 00:14:40.520
Wang and the others also sampled

00:14:40.520 --> 00:14:42.320
Ma Jinguang's DNA in the cabin.

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:43.120
They also found

00:14:43.120 --> 00:14:45.080
explosive materials from the same source

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:46.040
as the bomb that killed Zhang Biao.

00:14:46.040 --> 00:14:47.700
I think the murderer is Ma Jin.

00:14:50.880 --> 00:14:51.640
Doctor,

00:14:51.800 --> 00:14:52.720
how is my brother?

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:54.960
We have done a full-body and brain examination on the patient.

00:14:54.960 --> 00:14:56.240
Fortunately, everything is normal.

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:58.200
There are only some abrasions and soft tissue contusions,

00:14:58.200 --> 00:14:59.600
with no damage to internal organs or bones.

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:01.120
The coma is just a stress response.

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:02.760
He can be discharged after 24 hours of observation.

00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:03.360
Thank you.

00:15:03.560 --> 00:15:05.020
Thanks for your hard work.

00:15:15.200 --> 00:15:16.660
Before he fell into a coma,

00:15:17.160 --> 00:15:18.220
Old Yan told me that

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:21.490
the explosives that killed our master

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.120
were made by Ma Jinguang.

00:15:25.640 --> 00:15:26.570
He also said that

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:28.240
Ma Jinguang

00:15:28.480 --> 00:15:30.160
had nothing to do with Wang Hongjia.

00:15:30.160 --> 00:15:31.420
Nothing to do with him?

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:33.240
They were both in the mine.

00:15:33.240 --> 00:15:34.720
How could it be unrelated?

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:36.360
Besides, with so much evidence,

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:38.160
the killer has to be Ma Jinguang.

00:15:38.400 --> 00:15:39.130
I don't know.

00:15:40.920 --> 00:15:42.400
After that, he fell into a coma.

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:43.040
Master.

00:15:44.200 --> 00:15:45.320
With so much evidence now

00:15:45.320 --> 00:15:46.520
all pointing to Ma Jinguang,

00:15:46.520 --> 00:15:48.040
he has to be the killer.

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:50.500
Then...

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:52.170
could it be that Brother Yan

00:15:52.200 --> 00:15:54.200
hadn't finished what he was saying?

00:16:05.240 --> 00:16:06.440
Who exactly is he?

00:16:54.160 --> 00:16:55.600
Help!

00:16:55.760 --> 00:16:56.960
I won't say anything.

00:17:13.599 --> 00:17:14.599
Help!

00:17:32.960 --> 00:17:34.160
I've done everything

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:35.160
you told me to.

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:36.080
Good,

00:17:36.480 --> 00:17:37.480
but not enough.

00:17:38.160 --> 00:17:39.560
Should we continue then?

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:40.760
Of course.

00:18:11.840 --> 00:18:15.120
The machine has started.

00:18:16.560 --> 00:18:20.200
Nothing can stop it.

00:18:21.120 --> 00:18:22.480
No one can stop it.

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:25.040
No one.